KORNFELD--Allan. Retired President of Health Insurance Plan (HIP) of New York, formerly of Westbury, NY on January 17th. Beloved husband of the late Matilda R. Kornfeld. Cherished father of Nancy and Edward Sooper, of Hudson, MA, and Andrew and Christina Kornfeld, of Jupiter, FL. Devoted grandfather of Marika and Christopher Bruell, of Boston, Siri Schwartzman, of Cambridge, MA, and Reece and Trey Kornfeld of Jupiter, FL. Loving brother of Sally Weiss, of Manhattan. Burial will be private. Friends are welcome at 150 East 61st Street, New York on Friday after 4pm.
